path.desc: This is a description of district-n1. In other words, the res-nat quarantine zone where nat administers periodic whipping to res for no particular reasons other than the feelgood factor. path.desc: This is a description of district-n2. This is the brainworm factory, or, as some have come to call it the horny corner. It is a most despicable corner of Alexandria filled with the unadulterated brain juices of those who always let their thoughts run ahead of their keyboards and rack up dozens upon dozens of sheet/thread debt. Alas, Alexandria does not have an adequate sewage system to contain this brand of filth in particular.;https://cdn.discordapp.com/emojis/764198114356625439.webp
